# READ ME TRPO step 2

The instructions are the same of the READ_ME of TRPO of step 1. The only different thing is the fact that
in this case the values of the dynamic parameters thigh, leg and foot change for every episode.

In order to apply this, custom_hopper.py was modified. 
If you want to change the bounds of the uniform distributions, open the custom_hopper.py file and go to line 39. This file in inside the folder env. 
Torso is not sampled. 

After, for training and test the TRPO with UDR, follow the READ_ME of TRPO in step 1. 
